c: 10
v: 3
t: "Your Lord is certainly God Who created the skies and the earth in six periods, then He set the balance on the throne (of the universe), directing the affair. No mediator (can recommend) without (obtaining) His permission. That is God your Lord, so serve Him. Will you not then mind? without (obtaining) His permission. That is God your Lord, so serve Him. Will you not then mind"